p: The intermolecular interactions between metabolites extracts and the active residues of peroxiredoxin 5 have been investigated using the AutoDock package [ 50]. The starting geometries of peroxiredoxin 5 and the original docked ligand benzoic acid were downloaded from the RCSB data bank web site: human peroxiredoxin 5 enzyme (PDB code 1HD2) [ 51], human progesterone (PDB code 4OAR) [ 46], human androgen receptor (PDB code 1E3G) [ 52].
